  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increasing covid infection in the country",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Health has informed that 131 cases of Covid-19 have been identified in the country on Thursday.",
        "So far, a total of 665,248 Covid-infected people have been identified in the country.",
        "Meanwhile, no casualties were reported yesterday. So far 16,548 people have died due to covid infection in the country."
      ],
